"smart_blocks:Spring Proxy이용.md#Spring Framework 5.3 + Apache HttpClient 기반 실무용 `Advisor` 예제#이 구조의 핵심은 **AOP는 “대상 판정”**, **Apache HttpClient는 “실제 네트워크 설정”**을 담당하게 분리하는 것입니다. Spring AOP의 `Advisor`는 Pointcut + Advice 조합으로 특정 메서드에 공통 정책을 적용하는 용도에 적합합니다. ([Home](https://docs.spring.io/spring-framework/docs/5.3.x/reference/html/integration.html \"Integration\"))": {"path":null,"last_embed":{"hash":"14g3pgg","at":1776931407298},"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.03066843,-0.02764599,0.00179258,-0.03167702,0.02787923,-0.0401118,-0.03826685,0.06404705,-0.0142926,-0.01220914,0.03058553,-0.01297944,0.06115936,0.06529099,0.08277713,0.0336315,-0.04691681,0.0406524,0.02280231,0.01358892,0.10394347,0.016316,-0.02369953,-0.04627643,0.01982241,0.08006199,-0.03784687,-0.04937552,-0.03612098,-0.12578999,-0.02560587,-0.04883336,-0.01941207,0.01304822,-0.06286851,0.04775323,-0.01792461,0.07236482,-0.02815355,0.00798228,-0.00060329,-0.01463464,-0.04414205,-0.02847857,-0.0364652,-0.0794054,0.03967298,0.0108098,-0.04078902,-0.04297769,-0.0572092,-0.02197307,0.00491092,-0.00584522,0.002599,0.01403739,0.05269507,0.04271004,-0.01375641,0.02213277,0.02444636,0.04554319,-0.23008978,0.09478585,-0.00738138,0.04671531,0.01016073,-0.03109731,0.03933013,0.02324669,-0.09554628,0.05869217,-0.02976259,0.03469998,-0.01099792,0.03617148,0.0119044,-0.00759254,0.02687563,0.00405568,-0.0260367,-0.00743629,-0.01616658,0.00109459,0.01971221,-0.00056192,0.01030743,-0.05914404,0.02875327,0.03494724,-0.05713893,-0.04088775,-0.00670458,-0.07222211,-0.01392953,0.02992762,0.01022987,-0.00980799,-0.12402196,0.11802639,-0.03942449,0.00816263,-0.00737689,-0.02374267,0.02666006,-0.0842675,-0.06944495,-0.03859961,0.02707027,0.05152332,-0.02715017,-0.05016085,0.00090447,-0.08268218,0.0034243,0.02542456,0.04697787,-0.00909126,0.03924308,0.02973144,-0.0120349,0.01142696,0.05116653,0.03931078,0.04272962,-0.06943718,0.00121395,0.01197351,0.07931585,0.07818672,0.03460809,0.01179358,-0.03745129,-0.04817578,0.009